name: Flavel & Neto
description: '''Flavel & Neto''' are a singing duo based in France specializing in Latin-based dance music, but greatly influenced by Angolan [[kizomba]] music. They are signed to Five Music label and are mostly famous with their singles "[[Eu Quero Tchu, Eu Quero Tcha|Eu quero tchu, eu quero tcha]]" and "[[Tatararatat√°|Pedida perfeita (Tararatata)]]", the latter featuring [[Anna Torres]].
